<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <MadCap:snippetText src="PulseDashLoginAdminEmployee.flsnp" />
            </li>
            <li>From the menu bar, select <span class="Emphasis">Groups &gt; Owned by Me</span>.</li>
            <li>In the&#160;Find Groups page, click the desired group to open its page.</li>
            <li>
                <p>Under the <span class="Emphasis">Invites</span> area, click the <span class="Emphasis">Invite People</span> link. </p>
                <p>
                    <img src="../../../../Images/Shared/Fl-Pu/pulse_groups_invite_people.png" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
                </p>
                <p>This opens the Invite People dialog. </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>In the Invite People dialog, you can invite people by doing the following:</p>
                <ol class="LowerAlpha">
                    <li>
                        <p>In the Invite People dialog, click a user or group name in the box. </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>Place a check mark next to the users or groups to invite.</li>
                    <li>Click <span class="Emphasis">Invite</span>.</li>
                    <li>
                        <p>If the people do not have access to the feed, click <span class="Emphasis">Grant Access</span>. </p>
                        <p>This sends an invite to the person you added.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>